Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.64,0:00:48.69,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(150,150)}记忆如花瓣般衰败消散
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.86,0:01:00.37,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,150)}触碰的瞬间 破碎散落
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:08.33,OPch,,0,0,0,,{\blur4\fad(150,150)}带我走吧!
